These are the areas:
                               @{"Menu" link ShowMenu}
                               @{"Table" link ShowTable}
                               @{"Graph" link ShowGraph}
                               @{"Stats" link ShowStats}
                               @{"Wheeling" link ShowWheel}

To move between the screens, click on the @{"Screen" link ShowMenu} button near the top of the
screen, or use the Show Called Numbers @{"pull-down menu" link Pulldown}
@endnode
@node ShowMenu
@title "Show Called Numbers - Menu"
These options are available after clicking on "screen" in @{"Show called
numbers" link Show}

                               @{"Table" link ShowTable}
                               @{"Graph" link ShowGraph}
                               @{"Stats" link ShowStats}
                               @{"Wheeling" link ShowWheel}
                               @{"Exit" link MainMenu}

If you are using the @{"predicted" link Prediction} numbers, moving between the areas like this
